"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/820939","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","false","2018-01-18","<p>I refer my Hon. Friend to my answer of 11 January 2018 (PQ 120721).</p>","North East Bedfordshire","Alistair Burt","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/820939/answer",,,,,,"2018-01-18T17:13:31.433Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/820939/answer","Biography information for Alistair Burt","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/820939/answer",,,,,"16","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","2018-01-11","Israel: Gaza","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Foreign and Commonwealth Affairs, what recent reports he has received on rocket fire into Israel from Gaza.","false","Biography information for Nigel Huddleston","Mid Worcestershire","Nigel Huddleston","122357"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/820940","Department of Health and Social Care","false","2018-01-19","<p>The Government corresponded with the Government of the Republic of Ireland in early 2017 in relation to the cost-effectiveness of Orkambi for the treatment of cystic fibrosis.</p>","Winchester","Steve Brine","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/820940/answer",,,,,,"2018-01-19T14:19:09.23Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/820940/answer","Biography information for Steve Brine","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/820940/answer",,,,,"17","Health and Social Care","Health and Social Care","2018-01-11","Orkambi: Republic of Ireland","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health and Social Care, whether he has had recent discussions with his Irish counterpart on the cost-effectiveness of Orkambi in treating cystic fibrosis.","false","Biography information for David Linden","Glasgow East","David Linden","122358"
